metadata.name: MobyHeads #1
metadata.description:
Originally minted September 11, 2021 (migrated from the OpenSea Shared Storefront).

MobyHeads are a celebration of artistic freedom and expression! Our amazing design team at JoyPixels have been hard at work on MojoHeads, showcasing the rising stars of the art community. MobyHeads are sample designs to help conceptualize the final expressions.  My face was volunteered for the sample designs and it made sense to mint these after how great they turned out.

Thank you for all the love and support. ❤️

-Moby.eth
